verbose_text: All seven hESC lines had similar biological characteristics regardless of karyotype (five normal and two abnormal), such as expression of stage specific embryonic antigen (SSEA)-4, tumor-rejection antigen (TRA)-1-81 and TRA-1-60 proteins, transcription factor octamer binding protein 4 mRNA, no detectable expression of SSEA-1 protein and high levels of alkaline phosphatase activity.
